Assumptions:
-> patient can see own appointments, cancel own appointments, delete own appointments (but it not delete appointment on the side of doctor)
-> doctor can see own appointments, cancel appointments, change date of appointment, delete own appointments (vice versa)
-> staff can add new appointment for chosen patient and for chosen doctor

Each user is separated from another and has own resources although some of its resources are actually shared under the hood.
For example if I delete appointment for patient, it is not deleted for doctor.


Pacjent:
- patients/{id}/details -> bez wizyt, same dane pacjenta (szczegółowe). GET, PUT, PatientDetailsDto
- patients/{id}/appointments -> lista wizyt pacjenta (ogólne), GET, AppointmentShortDto (data, status, id pacjenta, id lekarza)
- patients/{id}/appointments/{id} -> dane o wizycie (szczegółowe, w tym dane o lekarzu i pacjencie), GET, Appointment


Doktor:
- doctors/{id}/details -> bez wizyt, same dane lekarza (szczegółowe) GET, PUT, DoctorDto
- doctors/{id}/appointments -> lista wizyt lekarza (ogólne), GET, AppointmentShortDto
- doctors/{id}/appointments/{id} -> dane o wizycie (szczegółowe, w tym dane o lekarzu i pacjencie), GET, PUT (tylko niektóre kolumny, dotyczące samej wizyty), Appointment


Staff:
- patients -> wszyscy pacjenci placówki, GET, PatientSgortDto
- patients/{id} -> ogólne dane pacjenta GET, PatientShortDto
- patients/{id}/appointments -> lista wizyt pacjenta (ogólne), GET, PUT, CREATE (od razu tworzy dla lekarza), AppointmentShortDto
- doctors/{id} -> ogólne dane lekarza GET, DoctorDto
- doctors/{id}/appointments -> lista wizyt lekarza (ogólne), GET, PUT, AppointmentShortDto

    // correct format datetime: YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM